@node "1" "What is it?"

@{b}This is it:@{ub}@{line}
@{line}
@{jcenter}

This is a GUI for the Fileformatconverter Med2Xm.@{line}

@endnode

@node "2" "What does it do?"

@{jcenter}

Supported options:@{line}
@{line}
- Output@{line}
- Enhanced Output (More Info)@{line}
@{line}
For more information about the options use the documentation, which is included in the Med2Xm programmarchive!@{line}
@{line}
The Output button must be pressed for informationoutput!@{line}
@{line}
Sinc version 1.5 of the Med2Xm-GUI is you can use the PowerPC version of Med2Xm without any problems.@{line}

@endnode

@node "3" "What is needed?"

@{jcenter}

@{b}Requirements:@{ub}@{line}
@{line}
- Amiga@{line}
- A-OS2.0 or higher@{line}
- Med2Xm or Med2Xm.elf program@{line}
- *.med-files to convert@{line}

@endnode

@node "4" "Installation!"

@{u}Installation:@{uu}@{line}
@{line}
Copy the Med2Xm-GUI program on the place wherever you want to have it.@{line}

@endnode

@node "5" "Menu!"

@{b}Menu:@{ub}
@{line}
  Project/About@{line}
    Programmers info@{line}
@{line}
  Project/Quit@{line}
    Quit the MED2XM-GUI.@{line}
@{line}
@{line}
  Prefs/Load Med2Xm@{line}
    Load the MED2XM-Program@{line}
    (If you want to convert a File, yu have to load the Program!)@{line}
@{line}
  Prefs/Load@{line}
    Load the last safed configuration.@{line}
@{line}
  Prefs/Save@{line}
    Save the configuration@{line}
    (Saved options: Buttons, the directorys and the window-possition)@{line}
@{line}
  Prefs/AutoSave@{line}
    Save the setting automaticaly on quit the program.@{line}
@{line}
@{line}
  Control/Convert@{line}
    Same function as the Convert button. It starts the conversation.@{line}

@endnode

@node "6" "Probleme"

@{b}Problems:@{ub}@{line}
@{line}
@{B}1.@{UB}@{line}
If you have a PowerPC in your system, use direct the Med2Xm.elf for the executable. Otherwise the output doesn't work.@{line}
This is a problem by the taskmanaging. If a PowerPC is found while using the Med2Xm, the Med2Xm automaticaly use the elf code. The Med2Xm.elf send now the Information to the console but my program is waiting for output from Med2Xm itself.@{line}
So the output isn't displayed, but the file is converted anyway.@{line}

@endnode


